text: Veszprém is an administrative county in Hungary. The capital of Veszprém county is Veszprém. It is in the western part of the country. The county borders with Vas, Győr-Moson-Sopron, Komárom-Esztergom, Fejér, Somogy and Zala. In 2019, 341,317 people lived there. Its area is 4,463.65 km².
title: Veszprém County
